content:
Using our prior conversation, create a survey of questions to assess a team's current level of maturity as a high performing team. Make the questions thought provoking without obvious answers. THe questions should force self reflection, as well as strengths/weaknesses of the leader. 
 Again, without obvious answers that people will want to pick to make themselves look good or not pick on the leader. Use a scale of 4 options from strongly agree to strongly disagree.
